social_posts.post_text:
“a year changes you a lot.” 

I took a screenshot of this photo at the beginning of the year. February 11th, to be exact. I prayed for a year of growth, rediscovering, contentment, fulfillment, and health. Thank you Jesus for providing me with each of those. I started to see life through a new perspective. I truly fell in love with life again. I have met so many beautiful souls in this past year who have impacted my life tremendously and I feel so blessed to be surrounded by a great quantity of them daily. I traveled to many new places, stepped out of my comfort zone plenty of times, ate amazing food, met so many people, laughed until I couldn’t catch my breath, made beautiful memories, praised my Savior, loved on my family, and fell in love with cheer again. I feel so immensely blessed and content. I can’t wait to finish this year strong and begin a new chapter of my life. Thank you, 2022, you have truly been a blessing. 💌
